The working directory contains the folders "test" and "train", each of which contains the folder "Inertial Signals" containing the 128-feature raw data for accelaration and angular velocity for the test and training sets, respectively

R version 3.2.3, Ubuntu 14.04 LTS

## R functions written for solving the assignment

run_analysis.R - this is the main function. It calls the following functions:

##

assgn1.R - for solving part 1 of the assignment
assgn2.R - for solving part 2 of the assignment
assgn3.R - for solving part 3 of the assignment
assgn4.R - for solving part 4 of the assignment
assgn5.R - for solving part 5 of the assignment

## Additional functions

assgn1nosave.R - this is just an additional function invoked by assgn2.R,assgn3.R, and assgn4.R. 


